<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include ('../partials/head'); -%>
    <body>
        <div class="app">
            <%- include ('../partials/header'); -%>
                <!-- product-main-area-start -->
                <div class="product-main-area mb-70">
                    <div class="container">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-lg-9 col-md-9 col-sm-8 col-xs-12">
                                <!-- product-main-area-start -->
                                <div class="product-main-area">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-5 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 mt-20">
                                            <div class="flexslider">
                                                <ul class="slides">
                                                    <li data-thumb="client/img/product/<%= indexct[0].hinhanh %>">
                                                        <img src="client/img/product/<%= indexct[0].hinhanh %>"
                                                            alt="woman" />
                                                    </li>
                                                    <% indexct.forEach((el)=>{ %>
                                                        <li data-thumb="client/img/product/<%= el.tenha %>">
                                                            <img src="client/img/product/<%= el.tenha %>" alt="woman" />
                                                        </li>
                                                        <% }) %>

                                                </ul>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-lg-7 col-md-7 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
                                            <div class="product-info-main">
                                                <div class="page-title">
                                                    <h1>
                                                        <%= indexct[0].tensp %>
                                                    </h1>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="th">
                                                    <p>Thương hiệu: <%= indexct[0].tenth %>
                                                    </p>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="product-reviews-summary">
                                                    <div class="rating-summary">
                                                        <a href="#"><i class="fa fa-star"></i></a>
                                                        <a href="#"><i class="fa fa-star"></i></a>
                                                        <a href="#"><i class="fa fa-star"></i></a>
                                                        <a href="#"><i class="fa fa-star"></i></a>
                                                        <a href="#"><i class="fa fa-star"></i></a>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <div class="reviews-actions">
                                                        <a href="#">3 Reviews</a>
                                                        <a href="#" class="view">Add Your Review</a>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>

                                                <div class="product-info-price">
                                                    <div class="price-final">
                                                        <span>
                                                            <%= new Intl.NumberFormat('vi-VN', { style: 'currency', currency: 'VND' }).format(indexct[0].giatien)%>
                                                        </span>
                                                        <span class="old-price">$40.00</span>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="product-social-links">
                                                    <div class="product-add-form">
                                                        <form action="#">
                                                            <a href="/giohang?id=<%= indexct[0].masp %>">Thêm giỏ
                                                                hàng</a>
                                                        </form>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <div class="product-addto-links">
                                                        <div id="fb-root"></div>
                                                        <div class="fb-share-button" data-href="https://donghothoitrang.herokuapp.com/chitietsp?id=<%= indexct[0].masp %>" data-layout="button_count" data-size="large"><a target="_blank" href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdonghothoitrang.herokuapp.com%2Fchitietsp%3Fid%3D<%= indexct[0].masp %>&amp;src=sdkpreparse" class="fb-xfbml-parse-ignore">Chia sẻ</a></div>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-md-12">
                                            <p>
                                                <h4>Mô tả: </h4>
                                                <p style="  width: 100%; 
                                                            text-align: justify;
                                                            background-color: transparent;
                                                            border: none; overflow: hidden; 
                                                            word-wrap: break-word;
                                                            white-space: pre-wrap;
                                                            white-space: -moz-pre-wrap !important;
                                                            white-space: -pre-wrap;
                                                            white-space: -o-pre-wrap;
                                                            font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif;
                                                            font-size: 17px;
                                                            color: #000;
                                                            line-height: 25px;"><%= indexct[0].mota %>
                                                </p>
                                            </p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <!-- product-main-area-end -->
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-sm-4 col-xs-12">
                                <div class="shop-left">
                                    <div class="left-title mb-20 mt-20">
                                        <h4></h4>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="banner-area mb-30">
                                        <div class="banner-img-2">
                                            <a href="#"><img src="client/img/banner/12.jpg" alt="banner" /></a>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="left-title-2 mb-30">
                                        <h2>Đồng hồ và thời gian</h2>
                                        <p>Thời gian của bạn là hữu hạn, vì thế đừng lãng phí nó để sống cuộc đời của người khác</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="left-title-2">
                                        <h2>Những chiếc kim đồng hồ</h2>
                                        <p>Phần lớn mọi người dùng điện thoại để xem giờ, nhưng đồng hồ vẫn luôn mang vẻ đẹp và sức hấp dẫn riêng của nó.</p>
                                        <p>Việc đẩy kim đồng hồ chạy nhanh chẳng thể khiến bạn tiến lên phía trước</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-12">
                                <div id="fb-root"></div>
                                <!-- <script async defer crossorigin="anonymous" src="https://connect.facebook.net/vi_VN/sdk.js#xfbml=1&version=v11.0&appId=333424968148234&autoLogAppEvents=1" nonce="oxOi1s2e"></script> -->
                                <div class="fb-comments" data-href="https://donghothoitrang.herokuapp.com/chitietsp/?id=<%= indexct[0].masp %>" data-width="100%" data-numposts="10"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
               
                <%- include ('../partials/footer'); -%>
        </div>
    </body>
<script async defer crossorigin="anonymous" src="https://connect.facebook.net/vi_VN/sdk.js#xfbml=1&version=v11.0&appId=333424968148234&autoLogAppEvents=1" nonce="ykJCp0C3"></script>  
<script async defer crossorigin="anonymous" src="https://connect.facebook.net/vi_VN/sdk.js#xfbml=1&version=v11.0&appId=333424968148234&autoLogAppEvents=1" nonce="1WrrHR29"></script>

</html>